Greenberg;;42;;76;;R;;Roger Greenberg (Ben Stiller), a failed musician now making a living as a carpenter in New York, returns to Los Angeles to house-sit for his brother (Chris Messina). He is stranded there -- since he doesn't drive -- until his brother's assistant, Florence (Greta Gerwig), comes to his rescue. She is as much a lost soul as he is, and as the pair begin spending more time together, they form a significant connection -- giving Roger a much-needed reason to be happy.;;Drama,Comedy,Romance;;Noah Baumbach;;2010;;Ben Stiller,Greta Gerwig,Rhys Ifans,Jennifer Jason Leigh,Chris Messina,Susan Taylor,Merritt Wever,Zach Chassler,Mina Badie,Blair Tefkin,Mark Duplass,Jake Paltrow,Juno Temple,Brie Larson;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/greenberg